from sklearn.cluster import DBSCAN
In [10]:
db = DBSCAN(eps=30, min_samples=6).fit(points2)
core_samples_mask = np.zeros_like(db.labels_, dtype=bool)
core_samples_mask[db.core_sample_indices_] = True
dblabels = db.labels_
n_clusters_ = len(set(dblabels)) - (1 if -1 in dblabels else 0)
n_noise_ = list(dblabels).count(-1)

import folium as fo
longitude =  100.5538272857666
latitude = 13.734465925243732
station_map = fo.Map(
                location = [latitude, longitude], 
                zoom_start = 14)
latitudes = list(data.latitude)
longitudes = list(data.longitude)
labels = list(data.title)
n=0
for lat, lng, label in zip(latitudes, longitudes, labels):
    if dblabels[n]>=0:
        c='red'
    else:
        c='black'
    fo.Circle(
      location = [lat, lng],
      radius = 1,
      color = c 
     ).add_to(station_map)
    n=n+1
station_map
